query: SELECT DISTINCT pp.year, pp.month, COUNT(*) as records FROM propertyPrices pp JOIN districts d ON pp.districtId = d.id WHERE d.city = 'Berlin' GROUP BY pp.year, pp.month ORDER BY pp.year, pp.month;
